Detailed Description

Browser Launcher. It launches the Browser application embedded to download the required content. The operation can be cancelled with Cancel().

IMPORT_C TInt CBrowserLauncher::LaunchBrowserSyncEmbeddedL ( const TDesC &  aParams,
MDownloadedContentHandler *  aContentHandler = NULL,
TBrowserOverriddenSettings *  aSettings = NULL 
)

Launch the Browser embedded with the given parameters. The operation is synchronous, and waits until the Browser terminates. Be careful when using: it uses CActiveSchedulerWait!

Parameters:
aParams Parameters to pass to the browser through the OpenFileL method.
aContentHandler Implementation of the file based content handler.
aSettings Overridden user preferences. Ownership is not taken!
Returns:
Integer error value returned by the embedded Browser.
